title: Ancient Tomb of Balvra
story: Balvra is long dead, but people are still reluctant to come close to the tomb. Lately a giant hydra has made its lair here. The tomb of Balvra is a place of growth of a valuable specie of fungi.

notes.text: A great stone gate with a keyhole on the southern wall of the large chamber.
A medium strongbox containing some gold.
A crown-shaped key tucked under some debris.
A vorpal staff and a robe in a box.
